                        "block": "<p>Customers in the United Kingdom are serviced by our warehouse in Bedfordshire. We've worked hard to find the best possible shipping methods in the United Kingdom and receive great feedback from customers who appreciate our fast and reliable shipping.</p><p>We currently offer the following shipping options to the United Kingdom:</p><p><span>*Premium Next Day:</span> This service is available for a flat rate of £3.49 and provides delivery Monday - Friday.</p><p><span>Standard (1 - 3 Business Days):</span> Using this shipping option, most packages arrive within three business days for a flat rate on £1.99 for all orders under £29.00, but is FREE for orders that exceed £29.00. Orders sent using Standard shipping are delivered Monday - Friday, excluding bank holidays.</p><p><span>*Nominated Time:</span> If you place your order before 7:00pm using Nominated Time shipping, you can receive your order the next day before 10:00am for £12.99 or before noon for £6.99.</p><p><span>*Nominated Date:</span> Using this shipping option, you can select your preferred delivery date up to seven days in advance for only £3.49.</p><p><span>Click to Collect:</span> If the Click to Collect shipping option is selected, your order is sent using CollectPlus. For more information on CollectPlus, please visit the CollectPlus FAQ page.</p><p>* These services are not available in the Highlands, Islands, Northern Ireland, and excludes bank holidays.</p><p>In accordance with the laws governing members of the E.U., Bodybuilding.com is obligated to charge Value Added Tax (VAT) on all orders delivered to the United Kingdom, however VAT is automatically calculated and included in the price of the products.</p>"
